library(ggthemes)

Read Data

# hnstats <- read_csv("bq-hnactivity.stats.csv")

interval.format <- "%F %H:%M:%OS UTC"

created.format <- "%F %H:%M:%S UTC"

hnstats <- read_csv("bq-hnactivity.stats.csv",

                    locale = locale(tz='UTC'),

                    col_types=cols(

                      task_id = col_character(),

                      story_id = col_character(),

                      story_createdat = col_datetime(format=created.format),

                      story_point_begin = col_integer(),

                      story_point_delta = col_integer(),

                      interval_begin=col_datetime(format=interval.format),

                      interval_end=col_datetime(format=interval.format),

                      comment_count_begin = col_integer(),

                      comment_count_delta = col_integer(),

                      story_rank_begin = col_integer(),

                      story_rank_end = col_integer()

                    ))

hnstats$interval_duration = difftime(hnstats$interval_end, hnstats$interval_begin)

Summary

Remove outliers in terms of interval_duration.

INTERVAL_DURATION = as.difftime(15, units = "secs")

Îµ.interval_duration = as.difftime(0.01, units="secs")

hnstats %>% filter(

  interval_duration >= INTERVAL_DURATION - Îµ.interval_duration &

  interval_duration <= INTERVAL_DURATION + Îµ.interval_duration

) -> hnstats

hnstats

p <- ggplot(hnstats, aes(x=interval_duration)) +

     geom_histogram(binwidth = 0.001) +

     labs(title="Filtered Dataset: Distribution of Interval Duration (secs)") +

     theme_tufte(base_size = 15)

p


hnstats %>%

   ggplot(., aes(as.factor(story_point_delta), as.factor(comment_count_delta))) +

   geom_tile(stat="bin_2d", color="#c0c0c0") +

   scale_fill_gradient(low = "white", high = "steelblue",trans="log10") +

   xlab("story_point_delta") + 

   ylab("comment_count_delta") + 

   theme_tufte(base_size = 15) -> p

p


hnstats$date <- as.Date(hnstats$interval_begin)

utc_time <- strftime(hnstats$interval_begin, '%H:00:00', tz="UTC")

hnstats$hour_of_day_utc <- as.POSIXct(utc_time, format="%H:%M:%S", tz="UTC")

cal_time <- strftime(hnstats$interval_begin, '%H:00:00', tz="America/Los_Angeles")

hnstats$hour_of_day_cal <- as.POSIXct(cal_time, format="%H:%M:%S", tz="America/Los_Angeles")

hnstats %>%

   group_by(hour_of_day_utc) %>%

   summarize(daily_mean_sp_delta=mean(story_point_delta > 0)) %>% 

   ggplot(., aes(hour_of_day_utc, daily_mean_sp_delta)) +

   scale_x_datetime(date_labels="%I:%M %p") +

   geom_bar(stat="identity") + 

   ylab("Pr[Upvote]") + 

   theme_tufte(base_size = 15) +

   theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1)) -> p

p
